text:
Hi all,

How i add any custom form field on member_register ?

Thank you! :slightly_smiling_face:

```{% member_register "my_register"       
 email_label="Email",       
 password_confirm_label="Confirm Password", 
 password_label="Password",      
 submit_button_text="Save Password"      %}```
Yeah, no problem. I also built a quick test using the above array but was able to get into each object just fine. Might be something on HubSpot's end, sorry we couldn't solve it
